# Secrets — defense in depth. Audit (HEAD + git history) currently
# shows no committed secrets, but add the common patterns so a
# future "I'll just put my OpenAI key in .env for testing" doesn't
# silently land in a public commit. Update this list when you grow
# new secret-bearing files; it's cheaper to over-ignore than under.
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
!.env.sample
*.pem
*.key
!*.public.key
*.crt
*.p12
*.pfx
secrets.json
credentials.json
id_rsa
id_ed25519
id_ecdsa
*_rsa
*_ed25519
*.gpg-secret
.npmrc
.netrc
.aws/credentials

# Build
/build/
/tmp/
.claude/worktrees/

# Wails / Desktop
desktop/desktop
desktop/frontend/dist/
desktop/frontend/node_modules/
desktop/frontend/package.json.md5

# Web companion (granit web). The SvelteKit SPA is built into
# internal/serveapi/dist/ and embedded by go:embed at compile time.
# Re-built by `make build`, so we don't track the artifact in git.
internal/serveapi/dist/
web/node_modules/
web/.svelte-kit/
web/build/
web/.vite/
